data.description: 3 bed 2.5 bath home in VERRADO! Upgraded Kitchen with all appliances -Gas stove and granite counters in this beautiful kitchen. Upstairs, you will find the master bedroom with full bathroom & 2 bedrooms with a full bathroom, . . Master bath has shower...master bedroom has 2 closets. YES- HIS & HERS! Master bedroom has walk on large patio that overlooks the huge green space in front of the house- Laundry room and loft area upstairs. HOA maintains the grass. Not you!  This great locations in Verrado offers - 2 community pools, numerous parks and miles of walking trails! !  Close walk to Heritage Community Pool and Heritage Elementary and Middle School.
